long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Automatically import your course schedule from Testudo to Google Calendar. 

This extension supports all semesters from Fall 2023 to Fall 2025. 

FAQs:
Q: Who is this extension for?
A: This extension is for students enrolled at the University of Maryland, College Park

Q: What if I update my schedule during the Schedule Adjustment Period?
A: No problem! Simple import your schedule again using the extension and a new calendar with your updated classes will be created for you in Google Calendar.
